### Get All Users
# Returns all users (passwords excluded).
# Requires a valid Bearer JWT in Authorization header.
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/user
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

###

### Get User By ID
# Returns a single user by their UUID (passwords excluded).
# Requires a valid Bearer JWT in Authorization header.
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/user/{{USER_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

###

### Delete User (admin only)
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/api/user/{{USER_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

###

### Update User Role (admin only)
PATCH {{BASE_URL}}/api/user/{{USER_ID}}/role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

{
  "role": "user"
}

###

### Reset User Password (admin only)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/user/{{USER_ID}}/reset-password
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}
